\b0 Problem Statement(Problem to be solved)                       One of the major problems in \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab today's world is that parents are not \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab able to their children all the time.  A \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab technological solution for this problem \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab will be wearable devices for children \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab so that parents will come to know \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab about all the activites of their children \par
Idea/Solution/Description\tab\tab\tab\tab Aiming at the increasing risk of \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab children, Mobile Children Security \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab Monitoring(MCSM) can be developed. \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab This can keep children in guardian's \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab view by using Bluetooth Near Field \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab Communication. \par
Novelty/Uniqueness\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab Iot enables to automate the child \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab monitoring and it also reduces cost.  It \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab eradicates the situation that the \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab parent should be physically present in \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab the particular place to monitor the \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab child.  It has high reliablity, short \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab response time and high accuracy.\par
Social Impact/Customer satisfaction \tab\tab\tab Due to the abusements the emotional \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab and mental stability of the children \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab gets affected.  It would create an \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab impact ont he entire growth of the \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab nation.\par
Business Model(Revenue model)\tab\tab\tab Focuses on capturing and delivering \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab value.  leverages the unique \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab characteristics of IoT products of \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab having 24/7 connectivity to \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab children by the parents and produces \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab innovative and differential value.\par
Scalability of Solution\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab Scalability issues can be sorted out \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab using IoT provided that the wireless \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab network is wide range with high data \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab speed and flexible software \tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab\tab infrastructure.\par
